## types.Unique type

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type Unique<T extends any[], ACC extends any[] = []> = T extends [
    infer F,
    ...infer RT
] ? IndexOf<ACC, F> extends -1 ? Unique<RT, [...ACC, F]> : Unique<RT, ACC> : ACC;
```
